        },
        {
          "id": "6ef534353175",
          "name": "1.3 控制流",
          "content": "条件语句：\nif-elif-else 结构。Python 使用缩进表示代码块。\n循环语句：\n- for 循环：遍历可迭代对象\n- while 循环：条件为真时执行\n重点：break 终止循环，continue 跳过本次迭代。",
          "level": 3,
          "importance": "low",
          "sources": [
            {
              "file_name": "examples/demo_notes.md",
              "page": null,
              "slide": null,
              "paragraph": 21,
